'''Israel Reyes Romero''' (born 23 May 2000) is a Mexican professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)#Centre-back|centre-back]], [[Defender (association football)#Full-back|right-back]] and [[Midfielder#Defensive midfielder|defensive midfielder]] for [[Liga MX]] club [[Club América|América]] and the [[Mexico national football team|Mexico national team]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Israel Reyes Romero |url=https://ligamx.net/cancha/jugador/108788/eyJpZENsdWIiOiAxMTU1MH0=/israel-reyes-romero |access-date=5 December 2021 |website=LigaMX.net |publisher=LIGA BBVA Bancomer MX}}</ref><ref name="Soccerway">{{cite web|title=Israel Reyes Romero |url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/israel-reyes-romero/618381/ |website=Soccerway |access-date=10 April 2026}}</ref>

==Club career==
===Atlas===
Reyes commenced his career in the youth academy of [[Atlas F.C.|Atlas]]. He made his professional debut on 30 July 2019, in a match that ended in a draw against [[C.F. Pachuca|Pachuca]]. Four months later, he made his league debut as a substitute in a 2–0 loss to [[C.F. Monterrey|Monterrey]].

===Puebla===
In the summer of 2020, Reyes joined [[Club Puebla|Puebla]] on a loan. He faced obstacles in getting playing time during his first tournament, but eventually established himself and secured a permanent transfer.

===América===
On 1 December 2022, Reyes signed with [[Club América|América]].

==International career==
Reyes received his first call-up to the [[Mexico national football team|senior national team]] by [[Gerardo Martino]], and made his debut on 8 December 2021 in a friendly match against [[Chile national football team|Chile]], coming in as a substitute in the 65th minute for [[Jordan Silva]].<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.fanbolero.com/2021/12/checa-la-convocatoria-de-mexico-para-enfrentar-a-chile/|title= ¡Checa la convocatoria de México para enfrentar a Chile!|website= fanbolero.com|date= December 6, 2021|access-date= 7 December 2021|archive-date= 7 December 2021|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20211207181234/https://www.fanbolero.com/2021/12/checa-la-convocatoria-de-mexico-para-enfrentar-a-chile/|url-status= dead}}</ref>

